===Notes===
Naming taboo ({{m|zh|避諱|tr=-}}); the last dot in 玄 was omitted to avoid using the same character in the {{w|Kangxi Emperor}}'s personal name, which was {{m|zh||玄燁}}, therefore producing {{m|zh||𤣥}}.

This was also applied to derived characters; characters like {{m|zh|弦}} and {{m|zh|畜}} were also missing the last dot in {{m|zh|玄}} during this time.

This also produced {{m|zh|𤍞}} < {{m|zh|燁}}.

